globus_cxx
==========

Build
-----

 $ autoreconf -if
 $ LIBRARY_PATH=/opt/gt5/lib ./configure
 $ CPLUS_INCLUDE_PATH=/opt/gt5/include/gcc32dbgpthr C_INCLUDE_PATH=/opt/gt5/include/gcc32dbgpthr LIBRARY_PATH=/opt/gt5/lib make

Run
---

 $ cd test/gram
 $ LD_LIBRARY_PATH=/opt/gt5/lib ./gram_ping_example `hostname`:2119/jobmanager:/O=Grid/OU=GlobusTest/CN=host/suguru-hamazakis-macbook-air.local 